homepage            https://dnsdiag.org

supported_archs     noarch
platforms           {darwin any}

checksums           rmd160  351cd25e55df0510124a2477e9132f5d7b2ecee3 \
                    sha256  b573a549522cd1b9299542ef424ba7692309c9d4c28c17ca935f6651b3f960fc \
